2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper uses multi-view data and performs experiments on image datasets, which are common in computer vision. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new model for density estimation and prediction, which are common tasks in artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses a generative adversarial network (GAN) architecture, which is a type of neural network. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper deals with missing views and updates its prediction, which is related to natural language processing tasks such as text completion and prediction.
